  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $3000<br />Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Jurong</p><p>Job Description:<br />•\tLeading warehouse assistants in daily operations.</p><p>•\tEnsure proper storage of goods and maintain good housekeeping.</p><p>•\tPerform cycle count & investigate inventory discrepancies.</p><p>•\tSupport warehouse tasks including SAP system transactions.</p><p>•\tCoordinate and collaborate within the team and with other departments.</p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in Logistics/Supply Chain/Business or similar w min 2 yrs of relevant order processing experience</p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p>allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>",
